headline.main: HARRIMAN BACK IN LONDON; Lease-Lend Administrator Has High Praise for British Industry

lead_paragraph: LONDON, Nov. 18 -- United States Lease-Lend Administrator W. Averell Harriman arrived today with a cheering message for the British, who, he said, are setting such a rapid pace in production of war supplies that Americans are finding it the hardest sort of job to keep up.
